      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WAHOO BLUE (6) was thereabouts on debut (18.87) at this track then improved nicely to get off the mark latest winning by one length (18.52) at this track. Won at his only start from this box. Hard to go past. GEORGIA'S MY MUM (1) ran above expectations to claim maiden two back then finished seventh last start and beaten 9 lengths at this track over 320m (19.00). Drawn well from box 1. Can feature with the right run. FAITH IN CAEDEN (2) jumps from box 2 again after finishing third (18.74) last time at this track over 320m. Safe beginner and drawn well close to the inside. Rates a leading chance. AVOCA MADNESS (8) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
